  "prompt": "What do Shahrukh Khan and Sahid Kapoor use on their hair?",
  "response": "As of the latest public information available, Shah Rukh Khan and Shahid Kapoor, like many celebrities, are known to maintain their hair with professional care routines, but specific products they use aren\u2019t always disclosed publicly. Celebrities often work with personal hairstylists and may use high-end or custom hair care products. \n\nHere\u2019s what is generally known or speculated:\n\n1. **Shah Rukh Khan**:  \n   - He has been associated with brands like *Pantene* in the past, endorsing their hair care products. However, his personal hair care routine likely includes professional-grade shampoos, conditioners, and styling products tailored to his hair type.  \n   - He is often seen with well-maintained hair, which suggests regular trims, treatments, and possibly heat protectants for styling.\n\n2. **Shahid Kapoor**:  \n   - Shahid has been a brand ambassador for *Gillette* and other grooming products, but his specific hair care routine is not publicly detailed.  \n   - He is known for his stylish looks, which might include products like hair wax, gels, or serums for styling and maintenance.\n\nFor both celebrities, their routines likely include:  \n- **High-quality shampoos and conditioners** suitable for their hair type.  \n- **Hair oils or serums** for nourishment and shine.  \n- **Styling products** like wax, pomade, or hairspray for their on-screen and off-screen looks.  \n- **Professional treatments** such as keratin treatments or deep conditioning to maintain healthy hair.\n\nIf you\u2019re looking to replicate their styles, consulting a professional hairstylist and using premium hair care products tailored to your hair type is a good start.",
